description: Israel expanded evacuation orders in Rafah as their offensive in southern Gaza appears imminent. Residents said there is nowhere safe to go, and President Biden said that the U.S. will withhold arms shipments if Israel invades Rafah. NBC News’ Hala Gorani reports.
title: Israeli offensive in Rafah appears imminent as residents say there is nowhere safe to go

description: Police were seen forcibly removing pro-Palestinian demonstrators at a protest outside the Malmo Arena ahead of the Eurovision Song Contest final. Thousands gathered in the city earlier to protest against Israel’s participation in the competition.
title: Pro-Palestinian protesters clash with police outside Eurovision venue
